    "name": "Thronefall",
    "steam_appid": 2239150,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Thronefall》是一款极简主义策略游戏，你需要在白天建设自己的小小王国，夜晚抵御来袭之敌。加固城墙、招募单位，亲自冲锋陷阵，在经济与防御之间取得平衡，抵御源源不断的攻击者波次，守护你的要塞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >既可以快速游玩，也可以来一场防守马拉松，尽情享受流畅、可反复游玩且充满意外的塔防体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/b75aa13b8c74b899f67cdc069c011fcc.avif?t=1772103797\" width=780 height=68 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10张地图。从群山环绕的北岩到生机盎然的野溪，逐步探索有不同地形、天气、敌人、建筑与挑战的多张地图。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9种可解锁武器。作为战士王者，你可以选择一样武器投入战斗，从战斧到血魔杖，应有尽有。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50多种可解锁特权。最多可携带5种特权以获得各种优势，还可选择变异以增加难度。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/f097c62433c81838298f558e359b3349.poster.avif?t=1772103797\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/f097c62433c81838298f558e359b3349.webm?t=1772103797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/f097c62433c81838298f558e359b3349.mp4?t=1772103797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/04f5ec754aebe1720bcbaa2918101d9e.avif?t=1772103797\" width=780 height=68 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用城墙、路障、神殿与塔楼守护你的王国。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过房屋、桥梁、金矿、港口、磨坊与田地扩展经济。这些建筑只要能安全度过夜晚，每天清晨都会产出金币。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过城堡中心、铁匠铺与皇家锻造厂研究升级。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用兵营、射箭场与英雄居所组建军队。你的部队包括骑士、狂战士、弩手、火焰弓手，还有魔像与法师等特殊英雄。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/a2b58d8414677db269a46d35f9959f64.poster.avif?t=1772103797\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/a2b58d8414677db269a46d35f9959f64.webm?t=1772103797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/a2b58d8414677db269a46d35f9959f64.mp4?t=1772103797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/7e80113db4f113b3aa1569e835b7513d.avif?t=1772103797\" width=780 height=68 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夜幕降临时，敌人便会接连来袭且越来越强，随时可能击溃你的王国。只有将敌人全部消灭，太阳才会升起。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >木桶骑士、飞行法师、食人魔、史莱姆、黄蜂与投石机，大地危机四伏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >城堡中心被摧毁即代表你被打败。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身为国王，你需要亲临前线，守护你的小王国，直至太阳再度升起。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/67de303c853162e6618a3caa91bdf151.poster.avif?t=1772103797\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/67de303c853162e6618a3caa91bdf151.webm?t=1772103797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239150/extras/67de303c853162e6618a3caa91bdf151.mp4?t=1772103797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你喜欢以下游戏，我们觉得你也一定会爱上《Thronefall》：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Total War: MEDIEVAL II, Age of Empires IV, Bad North, Kingdom: Two Crowns, Against the Storm, Banished, Townscaper, 9 Kings, Super Fantasy Kingdom, Ball x Pit, Diplomacy is Not an Option, The King is Watching, and Northgard</i></p>",
